                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d493">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Scruggs</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1892-08-29">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 29, 1892</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Adee requests a full report on the attack alleged to have been made on the
                    consul of the United States at Ciudad Bolivar, and his being wounded, and
                    informs him that, with a view to protecting American interests generally, a war
                    vessel has been ordered to proceed to La Guayra without delay.</p>
            </div>
